## John Scheiber - Communications Manager

After growing up as a BLC camper and attending Bear Lake Ministries, John served as a videographer and counselor for several summers and has a huge love for the ministry of Bear Lake Camp.

John now joins the Year-Round Staff with a desire to tell the story of camp through digital media. If you've seen some of our weekly recap videos in the last several years, chances are John was the creator! You will find him managing our socials, creating more content that will help share what God is doing at BLC, and helping with our worship music.
{% /twoColumns %}

---

{% twoColumns reverseOnMobile=true %}
## Trent Grable - Treasurer

Trent serves as Treasurer for the Bear Lake Camp board, bringing his financial expertise and heart for camp ministry to help ensure the long-term sustainability and wise stewardship of BLC's resources. With a background in accounting and nonprofit management, Trent provides invaluable oversight of the camp's financial operations. His involvement with Bear Lake Camp goes back many years, and his deep understanding of both the ministry's mission and its practical needs makes him an essential part of our leadership team. Trent is committed to transparency, accountability, and ensuring that every dollar serves the mission of challenging individuals toward maturity in Christ.

